{"tid":1547830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸證實831 太子站有死人，仲要唔止一個","createTime":"2019-09-06T20:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T21:16:27.000Z","uid":294505,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f49ca65c5ab834109b99f2579dda92f7edb2b60","tid":1547830,"uid":294505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqrDmZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqrDmZO.jpg&h=26b9c46b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係有研究開大陸打輿論戰嘅手段嘅話，就唔會對佢地施暴者扮受害者嘅手法陌生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家大陸吹風話有大陸人被打死，好明顯就係要喺事情敗露前引導同搶佔受害者角色。所以我地更肯定太子站係一定有人死！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而大陸吹得風，就知道紙包唔住火，但我地唔可以俾佢地得遑！大家要鍥而不捨咬住呢件事唔好放！講好左齊上齊落，生就要見人，死要見到屍！唔幫手足沉冤得雪衰過督灰！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e605d8ccc131642e452d811692350959fb9cd1b2","tid":1547830,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2572d0c1d49523f06ab72590f6eadf54500bf514","tid":1547830,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T20:38:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: